## Code Quality Requirements (All Phases)
- [x] Google-style docstrings on every module, class, and function
- [x] All user-facing strings use `self.tr()` or `QCoreApplication.translate()`
- [x] No raw SQL — SQLAlchemy only
- [x] No secrets hardcoded — all in [.env](file:///c:/Users/mxgs2/Workspaces/VSCode_Antigravity/Python/RES/.env)
- [x] Soft deletes only — no permanent data removal
